# EDAMAME for Claude Desktop - Developer Workstation Package

> **Master Repository:** `edamame_app` - See `../edamame_app/.cursor/rules/workspace.mdc` for workspace-wide rules.
> **Cursor rules:** Maintained in `edamame_rules` - run `../edamame_rules/setup.sh` to symlink.

## Project Context
EDAMAME for Claude Desktop bridges Claude Desktop transcripts (reasoning plane) to the
EDAMAME Security system-plane observer, enabling two-plane divergence
detection on developer machines.

This is a **public** repository. Do not commit private keys, internal URLs,
or unreleased feature details.

## Distribution Modes
- **EDAMAME app / posture CLI**: `edamame-posture install-agent-plugin claude_desktop` downloads and installs via HTTP+zip (no git/bash/python needed). Cross-platform.
- **Manual install**: `setup/install.sh` (bash) or `setup/install.ps1` (PowerShell) copies the package and renders config templates.

All paths use the same runtime code under `bridge/`, `service/`, and `adapters/`.

